our patrons and our researchers,

00:03:31.310 --> 00:03:33.920 position:56%
not only by recommending collections

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:36.130
by pulling the books
off the shelves,

00:03:36.130 --> 00:03:38.680
by letting them know
what treasures we have,

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:45.250
but also by having displays,
exhibits, programs, conferences,

00:03:45.250 --> 00:03:52.640
briefings, especially
one-on-one briefings.

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:55.580
We receive visitors
from all over the world

00:03:55.580 --> 00:04:00.010
who come to use our materials.

00:04:00.010 --> 00:04:06.940 position:56%
We work with different universities,
government agencies and others.

00:04:06.940 --> 00:04:12.290
