collections come alive,

00:04:31.310 --> 00:04:35.020
through their own experiences,
through their photographs,

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:39.180
through the works that they have
done, and through their own passion

00:04:39.180 --> 00:04:44.310
for the countries they
have written about.

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:47.950
And so we have a case
in point today.

00:04:47.950 --> 00:04:55.420
