Ethiopia a few months before.

00:13:36.580 --> 00:13:41.440
So this was a time of war
and international aggression,

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:44.580
all issues of collective
security and peace,

00:13:44.580 --> 00:13:50.360
and having to protect the weak
from the strong, and the powerful,

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:52.120
all of these are relevant.

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:54.910
But most of all, I
wanted to write this story

00:13:54.910 --> 00:13:57.960
because it's a fascinating story.

00:13:57.960 --> 00:14:04.190
