There was some more British
government maneuvering while

00:48:00.740 --> 00:48:06.300
deciding when to go into Sudan,
but he goes into territory here.

00:48:06.300 --> 00:48:10.780
And now he's back in
Addis Ababa in 1941,

00:48:10.780 --> 00:48:15.170 position:56%
five years to the day after he left.

00:48:15.170 --> 00:48:19.010
So it's time for questions, is it?

00:48:19.010 --> 00:48:20.310
[ Inaudible Comment ]

00:48:20.310 --> 00:48:21.610
Pardon?

00:48:21.610 --> 00:48:22.910
[ Inaudible Comment ]

00:48:22.910 --> 00:48:25.120
Yes. So far so good.

00:48:25.120 --> 00:48:26.420
You're still following?

00:48:26.420 --> 00:48:28.570
[Laughter] So here he
